Pendulum Effect
 When you take damage from a card effect (except during the Damage Step): You can destroy this card, and if you do, any effect that would inflict damage increases LP by the same amount instead for the rest of this turn.

 Monster Effect
 When you take damage from a card effect (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card from your hand, and if you do, gain LP equal to the damage you took. Any effect damage you take becomes 0.
